NOTE: Track #06, "20th Century Fox Fanfare (w/CinamaScope Extension)" is the GENUINE ARTICLE, the Real Deal -- and I might add the ONLY place that I've EVER found the 20th Century Fox audiologo, ANYWHERE. Although it lasts only about forty seconds or so, be warned that the bass is so incredibly intense in patches that it completely overwhelms any speaker system I've ever played it on
